00:15:57.170 --> 00:16:03.100 position:56%
I didn't call it the Genome
Political History, which may have --

00:16:03.100 --> 00:16:05.190
[Laughter]

00:16:05.190 --> 00:16:06.530
&gt;&gt; Possibly you should have.

00:16:06.530 --> 00:16:08.450
&gt;&gt; Exactly, right.

00:16:08.450 --> 00:16:13.610
But I just had not expected the
