00:16:23.290 --> 00:16:26.330
&gt;&gt; You wanted to -- I'd like you
at this point to read a section

00:16:26.330 --> 00:16:28.220
of your book that I
think speaks to this.

00:16:28.220 --> 00:16:33.930
&gt;&gt; Actually, a funny story is I
