00:16:33.930 --> 00:16:35.800
up any section of the book and --

00:16:35.800 --> 00:16:37.410
&gt;&gt; And make it relevant.

00:16:37.410 --> 00:16:38.710
&gt;&gt; -- and make it relevant.

